th</a> defeats Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Sawyer\" title=\"Harry Sawyer\">Harry Sawyer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\"><img alt=\"House Tarth.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/32px-House_Tarth.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/48px-House_Tarth.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/64px-House_Tarth.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Potter\" title=\"House Potter\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a> defeats Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robin_Potter\" title=\"Robin Potter\">Robin Potter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\"><img alt=\"Loras Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a0/Loras_Tyrell.svg/32px-Loras_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a0/Loras_Tyrell.svg/48px-Loras_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a0/Loras_Tyrell.svg/64px-Loras_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a> defeats a man</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\"><img alt=\"House Tarth.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/32px-House_Tarth.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/48px-House_Tarth.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/64px-House_Tarth.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\"><img alt=\"House Connington.s