></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Caswell\" title=\"Lorent Caswell\">Lorent Caswell</a> (host)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\"><img alt=\"House Oakheart.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/32px-House_Oakheart.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/48px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/64px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Arwyn_Oakheart\" title=\"Arwyn Oakheart\">Arwyn Oakheart</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Rowan\" title=\"House Rowan\"><img alt=\"House Rowan.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Rowan.svg/32px-House_Rowan.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Rowan.svg/48px-House_Rowan.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Rowan.svg/64px-House_Rowan.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mathis_Rowan\" title=\"Mathis Rowan\">Mathis Rowan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\"><img alt=\"House Tarly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/32px-House_Tarly.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/48px-House_Tarly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/64px-House_Tarly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/32px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/48px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/64px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Late_arrival\">Late arrival</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><