House_Manderly.svg/32px-House_Manderly.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/48px-House_Manderly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/64px-House_Manderly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Wendel_Manderly\" title=\"Wendel Manderly\">Wendel Manderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mollen\" title=\"House Mollen\"><img alt=\"House Mollen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Mollen.svg/32px-House_Mollen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Mollen.svg/48px-House_Mollen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Mollen.svg/64px-House_Mollen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Hallis_Mollen\" title=\"Hallis Mollen\">Hallis Mollen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/32px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/48px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/64px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Fourteen <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark_guards\" title=\"House Stark guards\">Stark guardsmen</a>, including <a href=\"/index.php/Shadd\" title=\"Shadd\">Shadd</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Heraldry\">Heraldry</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Melee_at_Bitterbridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Heraldry\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/32px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/48px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x