.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Caron\" title=\"House Caron\">House Caron</a> - nightingales</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Penrose\" title=\"House Penrose\"><img alt=\"House Penrose.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/32px-House_Penrose.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/48px-House_Penrose.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/64px-House_Penrose.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Penrose\" title=\"House Penrose\">House Penrose</a> - quills</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Estermont\" title=\"House Estermont\"><img alt=\"House Estermont.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/29/House_Estermont.svg/32px-House_Estermont.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/29/House_Estermont.svg/48px-House_Estermont.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/29/House_Estermont.svg/64px-House_Estermont.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Estermont\" title=\"House Estermont\">House Estermont</a> - green sea turtle</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/32px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/48px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/64px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a> - crowned stag</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\"><img alt=\"House Connington.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/32px-House_Connington.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/48px-House_Connington.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/64px-House_Connington.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\">House Connington</a> - griffin</li>\n<li><a href=